The protagonist, Naoya, is a first-year in high school. He asks out Saki, a girl he has been in love with, and she agrees to be his girlfriend. He's currently on cloud nine. But then, a beautiful girl named Nagisa comes up to Naoya one day and tells him that she wants to go out with him. Naoya feels himself wavering because Nagisa is such a good girl, and he comes to a decision! A new kind of romcom from a rather unexpected decision is about to begin!
(Source: Crunchyroll)

The second season of Yakusoku no Neverland. Fifteen children escape Grace Field House, a false paradise, hoping for a chance at freedom. Instead, they encounter plants and animals they have never before seen, and are chased by demons. The outside world is so beautiful, and yet is almost too cruel to face. Even so, the children refuse to give up. They are guided in their search for better lives only by a message from Minerva and a pen Norman left behind in order to fulfill their promise to return to the House to save those of their family who are still trapped within.
(Source: Aniplex of America) Note: Episode 1 streamed early on Amazon Prime on Jan 7, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on Jan 8, 2021.
Isshou Hatarakitakunai Ore ga Classmate no Daininki Idol ni Natsukaretara

Rintaro Shido, a high school boy who aspires to be a full-time house-husband, is in the same class as Rei Otosaki, the center of the popular idol group "Millefeuille Stars." The two have never been involved with each other, until one day when Rei nearly collapses from hunger, and Rintaro makes a home-cooked meal to feed her.......

"I'll pay you 300,000-yen a month. Can I come and eat with you every day?"

Thus began their new relationship, almost like a couple living together. Rintaro is unable to grasp the proper distance between himself and Rei, who comes to his room where he lives alone. There, Rei shows a vulnerable side that she would never show in the classroom or on stage.......?

This is the start of a romantic comedy about a semi-cohabitation arrangement with a beautiful, popular idol girl, that will make your heart tingle and pound!

(Source: Over-Lap, translated)
